{"id":178846,"type":6,"name":"局部","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/82/e4/178846_ay0Fb.jpg","summary":"《局部》跟随陈丹青的眼睛，洞见幽微辽阔的万华世界，欣赏名画细节精彩。陈丹青的眼睛，是这个时代最珍贵的艺术财富。本档节目，借由他的眼，他的语言，他的洞察与审美，讲述中西方名画名作的一个个微细的局部，一处处没有人注意到、但看过之后会恍然大悟、拍案叫绝的精彩细节。全片在陈丹青的画室拍摄，后期辅以大量的动画效果，通过年轻人感兴趣的话题、故事穿插引导，重新审视各时期艺术创作及艺术家被人们忽视的角落。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>看理想·局部</li><li><span>集数: </span>16</li><li><span>开始: </span>2015-06-15</li><li><span>结束: </span>2015-09-28</li><li><span>类型: </span>脱口秀</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>每集长: </span>25min</li><li><span>电视网: </span>优酷土豆</li><li><span>主演: </span>陈丹青</li><li><span>导演: </span>谢梦茜</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"综艺","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":629989,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629989","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"千里江山图","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-06-15","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629990,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629990","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"死亡的胜利","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-06-22","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629991,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629991","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"人民的胜利","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-06-26","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629992,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629992","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"初习的作品","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-07-06","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629993,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629993","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"巴黎的青年","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-07-13","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629994,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629994","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"谁养艺术家","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-07-20","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629995,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629995","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"绘画的放纵","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-07-27","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":629996,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/629996","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"非正式魅力","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2015-08-03","comme